<%- include("../partials/head", { title }) %>

<section class="rr-hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <p class="rr-hero-tag">not affiliated with osu! — 18+ only — for entertainment pls dont take this serious lol</p>

  <h1 id="hero-title" class="rr-hero-title">
    <span class="line1">find your</span>
    <span class="line2">osu soulmate</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="rr-hero-sub">
    a totally serious edating site for osu losers.... who want to find their osu soulmate..... arf meow meow brrr awruff
  </p>

  <div class="rr-hero-cta">
    <% if (me) { %>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/profile">setup your profile</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/browse">browse first</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/auth/osu">setup your profile</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/browse">browse first</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <p class="rr-hero-note">
    <b>18+ only.</b> if you’re under 18, please close the tab and go touch grass (respectfully).
  </p>
</section>

<section id="features" class="rr-features">
  <div class="rr-features-inner">
    <p class="rr-kicker">// how it works</p>
    <h2 class="rr-section-title">built different</h2>

    <div class="rr-feature-grid">
      <article class="rr-feature-card">
        <div class="rr-feature-icon">◎</div>
        <h3>find your perfect duo</h3>
        <p>filter by vibes (age + bio). browse one profile at a time so it feels less like a spreadsheet.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rr-feature-card">
        <div class="rr-feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>real time messages</h3>
        <p>send a message from browse. they see it in their inbox when they’re logged in. revolutionary.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rr-feature-card">
        <div class="rr-feature-icon">◇</div>
        <h3>your data, your choice</h3>
        <p>we store osu! username/avatar, age, bio, and messages. nothing wild. delete account is a future vibe.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rr-feature-card">
        <div class="rr-feature-icon">✿</div>
        <h3>community driven</h3>
        <p>the site is only as good as the people on it. tell your friends to stop stalling and make a profile.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("../partials/foot") %>
